3. Save this file as index.html.



2. Create the CSS File:

1. Open a new file in your text editor.


2. Copy the following CSS code:



body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f4f4f9;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

header {
    background-color: #008000; /* Green */
    padding: 10px 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 2.5em;
    margin: 0;
}

.container {
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

.footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 0;
    text-align: center;
}

3. Save this file as styles.css.



3. Upload to GitHub:

